    "note": "A faceted berg — the peak that gives **code·berg** its name. Built from a single pentagon split by one vertical fold and a central sub-peak, it reads as mountain, prism, and cursor caret at once. Minimum size 24px; keep clearspace equal to the width of one facet on all sides."
